         <abstract id="aspace_47fda67d65b7cd4025b2de3f40a3c02d">This collection contains letters, recipes, certificates, programs, articles, correspondence, photographs, notebooks, and various published works, including poetry and a memoir, which document the life of Mary Bartlett Smith, Class of 1897.</abstract>
